Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,==================================TITLE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.78,0:00:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送給被殺害的占卜師羅珊的請柬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.61,0:00:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱庭之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.02,0:00:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然一時心血來潮來到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.55,0:00:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這樣真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.91,0:00:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引路的人在我們上船之後就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.85,0:00:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂...喂 維多利加!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.85,0:00:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.26,0:00:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然只顧自己吃 太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.06,0:00:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的肚子也很餓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.24,0:00:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們是憑著羅珊的請柬來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.48,0:00:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以晚餐也只有一人份
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.93,0:00:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.98,0:00:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去找點別的東西吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.55,0:00:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有帶什麼點心來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.68,0:01:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的頭腦所指示出的必要的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.02,0:01:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急食品套裝 也在那些道具之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.41,0:01:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們都被留在了學園裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.35,0:01:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為了你強詞奪理的犧牲品
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.27,0:01:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.45,0:01:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼強詞奪理...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.95,0:01:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼資格說...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.71,0:01:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麵包的話 給你這個強詞奪理的人倒也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.73,0:01:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.08,0:03:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一彌!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.06,0:03:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一彌!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起來 一彌!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.17,0:03:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本男兒 就應習得保護弱者的力量!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.91,0:03:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是帝國軍人的三兒子啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.96,0:03:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站起來 一彌!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一彌!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 叫你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個喜歡清算物品又滿口歪理的留學生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.41,0:03:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我起來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你說...我也會起來啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:04:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦...這裡是哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.86,0:04:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來用餐似乎已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.52,0:04:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒來之後 所有的人就都在這個大廳裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡 這裡是...哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門打不開!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.75,0:04:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 怎麼回事!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.97,0:04:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛! 什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.11,0:04:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城 有件事很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.44,0:04:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.68,0:04:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才在餐廳裡還有9個人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上我們就是11人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.69,0:04:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 現在卻有12個人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.11,0:04:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多了一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fn方正姚体\2c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}第2話 死者之魂推動遇難船
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.04,0:04:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 真的有12個人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.20,0:04:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.41,0:05:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個沒在餐廳裡出現過的人混了進來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.89,0:05:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個人把昏睡的我們搬到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.38,0:05:06.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人為什麼要這麼做?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.96,0:05:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱庭嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.97,0:05:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.57,0:05:13.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來 「野兔」就是那些孩子們了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.51,0:05:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.11,0:05:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,QueenBerry號嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有點印象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別碰那個東西!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.39,0:05:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這艘船 果然是...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.18,0:05:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊 不會錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.50,0:05:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.14,0:05:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在圖書館裡讀到過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.54,0:05:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鬼故事!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.49,0:05:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,QueenBerry號是沉沒於十年前的船
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.11,0:06:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者的靈魂不得安寧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.79,0:06:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每當暴風雨之夜它便會出現
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.40,0:06:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引誘生者上船作為活祭品 然後再次沉沒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.28,0:06:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你那是什麼反應啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為你是在講笑話 所以配合你一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.19,0:06:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我是很認真地...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.51,0:06:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.62,0:06:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停電?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.55,0:06:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.31,0:06:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維 維多利加?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.09,0:06:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.14,0:06:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.73,0:06:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加! 你在哪?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}快開燈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.79,0:06:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.05,0:06:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不 那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.67,0:06:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才應該還沒有這些字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.30,0:07:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「十年時光已逝 真是白駒過隙」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.82,0:07:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「這一次輪到你們了」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.21,0:07:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「箱子已經備下」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「來吧 野兔們 奔跑吧！」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箱庭之夜...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野兔...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.60,0:07:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「野兔追逐賽」可不是什麼有趣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.55,0:07:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們...才是野兔啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.24,0:07:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被那些孩子們殺掉的!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.35,0:07:33.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的 那扇門上了鎖...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那扇門已經安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.78,0:07:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷阱已經解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.96,0:07:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走 速度快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.01,0:07:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們 你們也快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是...是!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.84,0:08:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒 沒事的 維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.36,0:08:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟在我後面...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.72,0:08:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.95,0:08:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使有人橫屍在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.73,0:08:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她似乎也完全不在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.21,0:08:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等等我!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要用救生艇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.21,0:08:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在這麼洶湧的海上用救生艇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.54,0:08:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太危險了!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 大叔!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.52,0:08:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放 放開我!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在這艘船上 就要淪為野兔了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.98,0:08:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要放下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.39,0:08:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.73,0:08:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要丟下我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.19,0:08:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.57,0:09:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可...可惡啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都警告過你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.88,0:09:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.54,0:09:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼多人死去 維多利加卻還...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回憶起了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,植物園裡的維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洋娃娃般的維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.08,0:09:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神秘而不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.15,0:09:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加 你究竟是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休伊!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 他已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.81,0:10:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.43,0:10:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只不過去了趟甲板...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.31,0:10:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 屍體哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.81,0:10:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.92,0:10:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是幽靈...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.97,0:10:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們 野兔們回來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.08,0:10:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請喝水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.30,0:10:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我語無倫次了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫莫里斯 在蘇瓦爾外交部工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.80,0:10:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.63,0:10:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱莉•蓋爾 ...無業
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.81,0:10:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我父親擁有一座煤礦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:11:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫涅德•巴格斯塔 在英國從事話劇演員的職業
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好要在下個月的公演裡...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飾演殺人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.42,0:11:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該 該不會是你...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.73,0:11:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.74,0:11:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來自日本的久城一彌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.06,0:11:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著 這位是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.34,0:11:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她叫維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.21,0:11:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕我冒昧 我們是不是見過面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫里斯 你是不是該向乘上這艘船的年輕人們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.14,0:11:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將來龍去脈解釋清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.94,0:11:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你在說什...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.04,0:11:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那艘船模
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.75,0:11:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我的朋友正試圖去觸摸那艘船模時
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你向他發出了警告
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.59,0:11:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼會知道那個機關
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我認得這艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.95,0:12:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 這艘船正是十年前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.31,0:12:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1914年沉沒在這片地中海裡的QueenBerry號
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去 這艘船上載著被稱為野兔的孩子們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.01,0:12:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,髮色 瞳色和語言都不相同
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.23,0:12:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來自於世界各地的十一名少年少女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.06,0:12:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因成年人的某種目的而被選中的他們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.24,0:12:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這艘QueenBerry號上度過了一夜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.18,0:12:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天亮以後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.75,0:12:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受上司之命調查了這艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.71,0:12:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子們怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.96,0:12:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.65,0:12:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死於自相殘殺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.15,0:12:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「某個目的」究竟是什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.93,0:12:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼孩子們會...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.19,0:13:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是收回遺體罷了 詳細情況我也不知道!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.61,0:13:07.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他們為什麼會自相殘殺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.83,0:13:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.90,0:13:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船艙不斷進水 這艘船就這麼沉沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.91,0:13:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所知的鬼故事就是發源於此的 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.22,0:13:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈船QueenBerry號
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.95,0:13:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者們的靈魂將遇難船推上了海面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.39,0:13:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自那天起過了整整十年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.94,0:13:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為他們帶去死亡的成人們被集中起來 然後死去...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都完了 我們也會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.11,0:13:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 你又這麼笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.78,0:13:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.94,0:13:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.28,0:13:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在配合你的笑話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.61,0:13:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑話? 我可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.50,0:14:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈會寫請柬 你覺得這可能嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.93,0:14:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.73,0:14:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可 可是 這艘船的確沉入了海底
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.53,0:14:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們能不能用鼻子聞聞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.41,0:14:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這股氣味是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.17,0:14:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛塗上的油漆的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.03,0:14:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這葡萄酒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從標籤上來看 是1890年產
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.61,0:14:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釀造於30多年前的蘇瓦爾紅酒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.19,0:14:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 它的色澤卻還很鮮豔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.73,0:14:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香氣也很新鮮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.65,0:14:41.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這瓶酒的釀造廠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.34,0:14:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經毀於1914年夏季爆發的世界大戰的戰火 
之中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的酒早已買不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來 標籤...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.40,0:14:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是重新貼上的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.03,0:14:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要特地這麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.47,0:14:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還用問嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.03,0:15:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是為了完全再現原來的那艘船啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.22,0:15:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.13,0:15:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牆壁上的那面血書
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.32,0:15:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這間浸水的大廳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.29,0:15:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有屍體又消失到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.52,0:15:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其我多費口舌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.79,0:15:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如用讓你們都能看到的方式 重組混沌的碎 
片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.63,0:15:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我們從甲板回來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.12,0:15:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理所當然地進入了現在所在的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.25,0:15:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這是為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.94,0:15:31.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為門開著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.09,0:15:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他房間的門都關著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:36.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.88,0:15:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把那扇門打開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.73,0:15:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 這邊也有剛才的大廳...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們最初所在的是這個房間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.76,0:16:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是個很簡單的圈套
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.88,0:16:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這牆上的血書
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.79,0:16:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我重組混沌碎片所得到的結論
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.57,0:16:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匯出的答案 就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壁...紙?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.65,0:16:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.36,0:16:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將貼在預先寫好的文字上的壁紙一口氣揭下 
來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.93,0:16:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點動作在停電的空隙裡已經足以完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.78,0:16:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣 知道方法以後就很簡單了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.71,0:16:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 你果然好厲害啊 維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.74,0:16:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.20,0:16:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水聲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.99,0:16:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 進水了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.74,0:16:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快到無線電室去求救!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.31,0:16:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還在磨蹭什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.14,0:16:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和船一起沉入海底嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.72,0:16:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這艘船是QueenBerry號
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.88,0:17:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼要想到達無線電室 就必須先往下走一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.27,0:17:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 這艘船的構造怎麼這麼麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是電梯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.11,0:17:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.63,0:17:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找樓梯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.45,0:17:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加 來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.15,0:17:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是...什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.30,0:17:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 因為很危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把手給我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.52,0:17:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城 我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.72,0:17:44.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一被你指責就會特別生氣啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.79,0:17:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我只是擔心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的算什麼話嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這好強的乖僻女
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.91,0:17:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.13,0:18:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然連這種地方都有陷阱...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.39,0:18:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 各位 樓梯就在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.18,0:18:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很溫柔呢 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.07,0:18:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才不也拼命保護了那位女孩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.31,0:18:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我也沒做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是個男子漢大丈夫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.33,0:18:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是看到我們牽手的樣子罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.05,0:18:40.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.00,0:18:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下全完了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.06,0:18:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.94,0:18:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作快點應該還來得及
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.31,0:18:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.12,0:19:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上 上來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 快到我背上來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.39,0:19:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間猶豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你勒到我的脖子了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.57,0:19:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊 會死人的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.44,0:19:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你自己選擇背負的累贅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.17,0:19:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累贅?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.36,0:19:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說累贅了 這重量還不如旅行箱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.73,0:19:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子是這麼輕的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.01,0:19:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.47,0:19:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會是害怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.60,0:19:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.32,0:19:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.05,0:19:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:19:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.60,0:20:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何乖僻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.37,0:20:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維多利加畢竟是個女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.00,0:20:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個嬌小的 嬌小的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.08,0:20:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本 帶她來旅行的人就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.29,0:20:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.31,0:20:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本男兒 就應習得保護弱者的力量!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.11,0:20:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看 從這裡好像能上到安全地帶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.65,0:20:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 再這樣下去會變成野兔的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.90,0:20:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.27,0:20:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是為了不落到那種地步 才要到無線電室去 
的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.78,0:20:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒人來救援怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.07,0:20:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橫豎都要死的話 不如拉你們墊背
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.93,0:20:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你突然間幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.59,0:20:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.09,0:20:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 你適可而止啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.11,0:20:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這艘船上藏著很多武器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.86,0:21:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽屜裡 花瓶裡 地毯下 到處都是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.15,0:21:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.55,0:21:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓他們自相殘殺啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.07,0:21:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野兔們受到獵犬挑撥 開始互相懷疑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.85,0:21:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當他們發現武器之後 便開始自相殘殺!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.45,0:21:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獵犬?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.97,0:21:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 你們誰是野兔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.03,0:21:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野兔都死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.89,0:21:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.61,0:21:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有人活了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.53,0:21:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙現在正好就和你們差不多大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.03,0:21:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經什麼都不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.06,0:21:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我要把你們全都殺光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.85,0:21:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨自從這艘船裡逃出去!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.90,0:21:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫里斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.24,0:21:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這事和維多利加沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.74,0:21:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關係? 那種東西無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.82,0:21:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.30,0:21:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我絕不允許...你這麼做!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.61,0:22:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.13,0:22:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.84,0:22:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我邀你來的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.90,0:22:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為帝國軍人的三兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.86,0:22:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須保證維多利加你活著回去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.15,0:22:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有這樣的責任!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.36,0:22:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.17,0:22:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是野兔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.97,0:22:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.58,0:24:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野兔和...獵犬?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.27,0:24:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我什麼都不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.23,0:24:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人難以理解的還有你 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.75,0:24:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會如此為相識不久的我著想...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.47,0:24:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}下回 野兔們在朝陽下許下約定